hopobject.name: Page
hopobject.body: What do you do for a living? www.getcanadiandrugs.com/ They have one of the stars of the Top  14 in scrum-half Jonathan Pelissie. He has been simply sensational. He may be 27 and on his third club, having previously been at Brive and Grenoble, and, as is often the case in France, he can play at nine or 10. But he is clearly a late developer and has some serious pace, as he showed in a recent try against Toulouse where he skinned the France wing/fullback Yoann Huget.
